  m_Name: Inventory
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Title: The Inventory
  Description: "This cardboard box is the perfect home for your shiny new dice, or
    dice you simply don't wanna use. \n\ndragging them in from your precious egg
    carton and left clicking will drop them in, and you can take them out by left
    clicking them and dragging them into your egg carton. \n\nYou can also pull dice
    around in your inventory by holding right click, scrolling while pulling will
    increase the range."
